This file will explain a few of Dragonball truth's functions.

Basic Commands
--------------

help: help (filename) will bring up a help document on that file.
score: will display your current statistics.
status: will display such things as current trans, or hunger/thrist
status.
who: will display what VISIBLE players are on DBT. With differing
name colors for differing strengths in relation to the user of who.
Bold teal for players weaker then the user, dark teal for players
stronger, and green for players equal to the user.
where: displays all the players in your zone.

